
"smart_sources:_000.General/_000.General.md": {"path":"_000.General/_000.General.md","last_embed":{"hash":null},"embeddings":{},"last_read":{"hash":"kfr3xw","at":1772113914357},"class_name":"SmartSource","last_import":{"mtime":1772025355226,"size":22715,"at":1772113914366,"hash":"kfr3xw"},"blocks":{"#---frontmatter---":[1,8],"#":[9,10],"#_000.General":[11,228],"#_000.General#{1}":[13,13],"#_000.General#{2}":[14,223],"#_000.General#{3}":[224,228]},"outlinks":[{"title":"_000.General","target":"_000.General","line":14},{"title":"“A little learning is a dangerous thing; Drink deep, or taste not the c- There shallow draughts intoxicate the brain, And drinking largely sobers us again.” -Alexander Pope","target":"“A little learning is a dangerous thing; Drink deep, or taste not the c- There shallow draughts intoxicate the brain, And drinking largely sobers us again.” -Alexander Pope","line":15},{"title":"“Every time we say yes to a request, we are also saying no to anything else we might accomplish with the time.” -Tim Harford","target":"“Every time we say yes to a request, we are also saying no to anything else we might accomplish with the time.” -Tim Harford","line":16},{"title":"“Everything can be taken from a man but one thing - the last of the human freedoms  to choose one’s attitude in any given set of circumstances, to choose one’s own way.” -Viktor Frankl","target":"“Everything can be taken from a man but one thing - the last of the human freedoms  to choose one’s attitude in any given set of circumstances, to choose one’s own way.” -Viktor Frankl","line":17},{"title":"“He who has a ‘why’ to live can bear almost any ‘how","target":"“He who has a ‘why’ to live can bear almost any ‘how","line":18},{"title":"“How do I overcome procrastination Ice bath, cold shower, or simply 30 deep breaths in via nose out via mouth; get jittery, then get to it.","target":"“How do I overcome procrastination Ice bath, cold shower, or simply 30 deep breaths in via nose out via mouth; get jittery, then get to it.","line":19},{"title":"“I fear not the man who has practiced 10,000 kicks once, but I fear the man who has practiced one kick 10,000 times.”","target":"“I fear not the man who has practiced 10,000 kicks once, but I fear the man who has practiced one kick 10,000 times.”","line":20},{"title":"“I have seen the beauty of good, and the ugliness of evil, and have recognized that the wrongdoer has a nature related to my own.” — Marcus Aurelius","target":"“I have seen the beauty of good, and the ugliness of evil, and have recognized that the wrongdoer has a nature related to my own.” — Marcus Aurelius","line":21},{"title":"“If I had to do this today,tomorrow,  would I agree to it”","target":"“If I had to do this today,tomorrow,  would I agree to it”","line":22},{"title":"“If you can't figure out what kind of work you like, pay attention to what's easy to concentrate on and gives you energy vs. what makes you tune out and feel tired.”","target":"“If you can't figure out what kind of work you like, pay attention to what's easy to concentrate on and gives you energy vs. what makes you tune out and feel tired.”","line":23},{"title":"“If you feel that you just can’t write or you’re too tired or this, that, and the other, just stop thinking about it, and go and work. Life doesn’t have to be so overthought. You don’t have to wait to be inspired. Just start working.”","target":"“If you feel that you just can’t write or you’re too tired or this, that, and the other, just stop thinking about it, and go and work. Life doesn’t have to be so overthought. You don’t have to wait to be inspired. Just start working.”","line":24},{"title":"“It is remarkable how much long-term advantage people like us have gotten by trying to be consistently not stupid, instead of trying to be very intelligent.”— Charlie Munger","target":"“It is remarkable how much long-term advantage people like us have gotten by trying to be consistently not stupid, instead of trying to be very intelligent.”— Charlie Munger","line":25},{"title":"“It’s easier to practice self-restraint when you don’t have to use it.","target":"“It’s easier to practice self-restraint when you don’t have to use it.","line":26},{"title":"“Men move toward whatever makes them feel competent.”","target":"“Men move toward whatever makes them feel competent.”","line":27},{"title":"“The best thing a human being can do is to help another human being know more.” -Charlie Munger","target":"“The best thing a human being can do is to help another human being know more.” -Charlie Munger","line":28},{"title":"“The best thing for the human nervous system is another human – and – the worst thing for the human nervous system is another human.” _– Dr. Lisa Feldman_","target":"“The best thing for the human nervous system is another human – and – the worst thing for the human nervous system is another human.” _– Dr. Lisa Feldman_","line":29},{"title":"“The best thing for the human nervous system is another human – and – the worst thing for the human nervous system is another human.” – Dr. Lisa Feldman","target":"“The best thing for the human nervous system is another human – and – the worst thing for the human nervous system is another human.” – Dr. Lisa Feldman","line":30},{"title":"“The key to is to be able to find cheap and quick way how to try bad ideas.”","target":"“The key to is to be able to find cheap and quick way how to try bad ideas.”","line":31},{"title":"“The true measure of your education is not what you know, but how you share what you know with others.”","target":"“The true measure of your education is not what you know, but how you share what you know with others.”","line":32},{"title":"“The true soldier fights not because he hates what is in front of him, but because he loves what is behind him.” ― G.K. Chesterton","target":"“The true soldier fights not because he hates what is in front of him, but because he loves what is behind him.” ― G.K. Chesterton","line":33},{"title":"“There is nothing so useless as doing efficiently that which should not be done at all.”","target":"“There is nothing so useless as doing efficiently that which should not be done at all.”","line":34},{"title":"“To know your Enemy, you must become your Enemy.”    ― Sun Tzu","target":"“To know your Enemy, you must become your Enemy.”    ― Sun Tzu","line":35},{"title":"“When you wake up in the morning, tell yourself The people I will deal with today will be meddling, ungrateful, arrogant, dishonest, jealous and surly","target":"“When you wake up in the morning, tell yourself The people I will deal with today will be meddling, ungrateful, arrogant, dishonest, jealous and surly","line":36},{"title":"“You are going to pay a price for everything you do and everything you do not do. You do not get to choose to not pay a price. You get to choose which poison you are going to take. That’s it.” -Jordan B. Peterson","target":"“You are going to pay a price for everything you do and everything you do not do. You do not get to choose to not pay a price. You get to choose which poison you are going to take. That’s it.” -Jordan B. Peterson","line":37},{"title":"“You can’t learn that which you think you already know.” -Epictetus","target":"“You can’t learn that which you think you already know.” -Epictetus","line":38},{"title":"“You shouldn't be entitled to an opinion till you can argue the other side better.”","target":"“You shouldn't be entitled to an opinion till you can argue the other side better.”","line":39},{"title":"5 Ways to Build Resilience and Conquer Adversity","target":"5 Ways to Build Resilience and Conquer Adversity","line":40},{"title":"A man is about as big as the things that make him angry.","target":"A man is about as big as the things that make him angry.","line":41},{"title":"A man matures when he no longer believes discomfort is uncomfortable.","target":"A man matures when he no longer believes discomfort is uncomfortable.","line":42},{"title":"A man's hatred is always concentrated upon that which makes him conscious of his bad qualities","target":"A man's hatred is always concentrated upon that which makes him conscious of his bad qualities","line":43},{"title":"A real man doesn't give way to anger...The nearer a man comes to a calm mind, the closer he is to strength. –Marcus Aurelius","target":"A real man doesn't give way to anger...The nearer a man comes to a calm mind, the closer he is to strength. –Marcus Aurelius","line":44},{"title":"Adaptation in the biological sense, you only need to be as good as you have to be to get the outcomes that are important to you, not be the best parent that ever was.","target":"Adaptation in the biological sense, you only need to be as good as you have to be to get the outcomes that are important to you, not be the best parent that ever was.","line":45},{"title":"All the returns in life, whether in wealth, relationships, or knowledge, come from compound interest.","target":"All the returns in life, whether in wealth, relationships, or knowledge, come from compound interest.","line":46},{"title":"Allow yourself to make a garbage; Work on unprobable places.","target":"Allow yourself to make a garbage; Work on unprobable places.","line":47},{"title":"Anxiety is a call to action. It will continue to signal to us, robbing us of our potential peace until we make the changes it demands.","target":"Anxiety is a call to action. It will continue to signal to us, robbing us of our potential peace until we make the changes it demands.","line":48},{"title":"Anyone can make a subject complicated but only someone who understands can make it simple.","target":"Anyone can make a subject complicated but only someone who understands can make it simple.","line":49},{"title":"Anything done right is not trivial_","target":"Anything done right is not trivial_","line":50},{"title":"Arguing is not about proving other person wrong. Its about finding what is true and what we can do about it.","target":"Arguing is not about proving other person wrong. Its about finding what is true and what we can do about it.","line":51},{"title":"Ask person who holds opposite opinion, view what book, media was important for creating their opinion.","target":"Ask person who holds opposite opinion, view what book, media was important for creating their opinion.","line":52},{"title":"Ask questions to find out what your match is passionate about. What drives them For example, What's the most important value in your life right now' or 'What are your long-term goals and short-term goals","target":"Ask questions to find out what your match is passionate about. What drives them For example, What's the most important value in your life right now' or 'What are your long-term goals and short-term goals","line":53},{"title":"At lunch in a French restaurant, my friends ate the salmon and threw away the skin; at dinner, at a sushi bar, the very same friends ate the skin and threw away the salmon.","target":"At lunch in a French restaurant, my friends ate the salmon and threw away the skin; at dinner, at a sushi bar, the very same friends ate the skin and threw away the salmon.","line":54},{"title":"at the end of your career, the only people who are going to remember you worked overtime are your kids.","target":"at the end of your career, the only people who are going to remember you worked overtime are your kids.","line":55},{"title":"Avoiding Stupidity Is Easier Than Seeking Brilliance","target":"Avoiding Stupidity Is Easier Than Seeking Brilliance","line":56},{"title":"Be kind, for everyone you meet is fighting a hard battle you know nothing about.","target":"Be kind, for everyone you meet is fighting a hard battle you know nothing about.","line":57},{"title":"Before stepping away from your work, leave it in a state where it is Obviously wrong, but Easy to Fix","target":"Before stepping away from your work, leave it in a state where it is Obviously wrong, but Easy to Fix","line":58},{"title":"Before you work harder on something, identify the leverage point.  Working smarter is the most valuable form of working harder.","target":"Before you work harder on something, identify the leverage point.  Working smarter is the most valuable form of working harder.","line":59},{"title":"Being kind is most practical, selfish thing. Also superpower that can be cultivated and is likely rewarded in long term.","target":"Being kind is most practical, selfish thing. Also superpower that can be cultivated and is likely rewarded in long term.","line":60},{"title":"Being nervous - being excited","target":"Being nervous - being excited","line":61},{"title":"Big Brother isn't watching. He’s making sure you’re always distracted.","target":"Big Brother isn't watching. He’s making sure you’re always distracted.","line":62},{"title":"But when you do the hard things, life gets easier when you just do the easy things in life, life gets hard","target":"But when you do the hard things, life gets easier when you just do the easy things in life, life gets hard","line":63},{"title":"By mastering first principles, you can find better ways of doing things, instead of having to stick to conventions. Once you know the why of something, it is easy to modify the how to achieve your desired result.","target":"By mastering first principles, you can find better ways of doing things, instead of having to stick to conventions. Once you know the why of something, it is easy to modify the how to achieve your desired result.","line":64},{"title":"Caring is resource. Choose what you care about.","target":"Caring is resource. Choose what you care about.","line":65},{"title":"Children totally accept — and crave — family rules. “In our family we have a rule for X” is the only excuse a parent needs for setting a family policy. In fact, “I have a rule for X” is the only excuse you need for your own personal policie","target":"Children totally accept — and crave — family rules. “In our family we have a rule for X” is the only excuse a parent needs for setting a family policy. In fact, “I have a rule for X” is the only excuse you need for your own personal policie","line":66},{"title":"Clear your mind and get a hold on yourself and, as when awakened from sleep and realizing it was only a bad dream upsetting you. –Marcus Aurelius","target":"Clear your mind and get a hold on yourself and, as when awakened from sleep and realizing it was only a bad dream upsetting you. –Marcus Aurelius","line":67},{"title":"Coaching questions from 'The Coaching Habit’","target":"Coaching questions from 'The Coaching Habit’","line":68},{"title":"Comparison is the thief of joy. -Theodore Roosevelt","target":"Comparison is the thief of joy. -Theodore Roosevelt","line":69},{"title":"Compete, Create, Compete, Complete - 4 C's of motivation","target":"Compete, Create, Compete, Complete - 4 C's of motivation","line":70},{"title":"Compliment people behind their back. It’ll come back to you.","target":"Compliment people behind their back. It’ll come back to you.","line":71},{"title":"Consistent vs Persistant - Presistant to get it, Consistent to keep it","target":"Consistent vs Persistant - Presistant to get it, Consistent to keep it","line":72},{"title":"Degree you are able to let go is the degree you are able to let in things you actually want.","target":"Degree you are able to let go is the degree you are able to let in things you actually want.","line":73},{"title":"Depression is like a woman in black. If she returns, don't shoo her away. Invite her in, offer her a seat, treat her like a guest and listen to what she wants to say.","target":"Depression is like a woman in black. If she returns, don't shoo her away. Invite her in, offer her a seat, treat her like a guest and listen to what she wants to say.","line":74},{"title":"Discipline Eats Motivation For Breakfast.","target":"Discipline Eats Motivation For Breakfast.","line":75},{"title":"Do what you can do and don't stress about the rest.","target":"Do what you can do and don't stress about the rest.","line":76},{"title":"Domain dependance","target":"Domain dependance","line":77},{"title":"Don't let happiness depend on something you may lose.","target":"Don't let happiness depend on something you may lose.","line":78},{"title":"Don't make the past failure stop you from trying again","target":"Don't make the past failure stop you from trying again","line":79},{"title":"Dopamine is not about pursuit of happiness but happiness of pursuit","target":"Dopamine is not about pursuit of happiness but happiness of pursuit","line":80},{"title":"Downside of 80-20 principle- new path will never be most effective at the beginning. You need practice for getting better.","target":"Downside of 80-20 principle- new path will never be most effective at the beginning. You need practice for getting better.","line":81},{"title":"Dwelling extensively on your lack of results can also mislead you into thinking that you're somehow useless or defective, even when your failures are often just a reflection of you tackling harder challenges than others.","target":"Dwelling extensively on your lack of results can also mislead you into thinking that you're somehow useless or defective, even when your failures are often just a reflection of you tackling harder challenges than others.","line":82},{"title":"Easy win for entering flow","target":"Easy win for entering flow","line":83},{"title":"Eating is not giving us energy. Action does.","target":"Eating is not giving us energy. Action does.","line":84},{"title":"Effective learning Explain & Test","target":"Effective learning Explain & Test","line":85},{"title":"Environment matters","target":"Environment matters","line":86},{"title":"Eric Barker - Barking Up The Wrong Tree","target":"Eric Barker - Barking Up The Wrong Tree","line":87},{"title":"Every new frontier that can be conquered is an advance forward.","target":"Every new frontier that can be conquered is an advance forward.","line":88},{"title":"Expectation is driving our reaction on situation","target":"Expectation is driving our reaction on situation","line":89},{"title":"Experience is not what happens to a man; it is what a man does with what happens to him.  — Aldous Huxley","target":"Experience is not what happens to a man; it is what a man does with what happens to him.  — Aldous Huxley","line":90},{"title":"Fail early and get it all over with. If you learn to deal with failure you can have a worthwhile career. You learn to breathe again when you embrace failure as a part of life, not as the determining moment of life.","target":"Fail early and get it all over with. If you learn to deal with failure you can have a worthwhile career. You learn to breathe again when you embrace failure as a part of life, not as the determining moment of life.","line":91},{"title":"Feynman’s method for solving problems","target":"Feynman’s method for solving problems","line":92},{"title":"Focused vs Diffused mode of thinking","target":"Focused vs Diffused mode of thinking","line":93},{"title":"For the robust, an error is information; for the fragile, an error is an error.","target":"For the robust, an error is information; for the fragile, an error is an error.","line":94},{"title":"From note-taking to note-making","target":"From note-taking to note-making","line":95},{"title":"Gamify to do list,  project","target":"Gamify to do list,  project","line":96},{"title":"Garbage time with kids","target":"Garbage time with kids","line":97},{"title":"Goals are for people who care about winning once. Systems are for people who care about winning repeatedly.","target":"Goals are for people who care about winning once. Systems are for people who care about winning repeatedly.","line":98},{"title":"He robs present ills of their power who has perceived their coming beforehand.” —Seneca","target":"He robs present ills of their power who has perceived their coming beforehand.” —Seneca","line":99},{"title":"He that has once done you a kindness will be more ready to do you another, than he whom you yourself have obliged","target":"He that has once done you a kindness will be more ready to do you another, than he whom you yourself have obliged","line":100},{"title":"Help others to help yourself","target":"Help others to help yourself","line":101},{"title":"Holding onto anger is like drinking poison and expecting the other person to die.","target":"Holding onto anger is like drinking poison and expecting the other person to die.","line":102},{"title":"How not to lose a day anymore. Story of the day.","target":"How not to lose a day anymore. Story of the day.","line":103},{"title":"How To find motivation with ADHD","target":"How To find motivation with ADHD","line":104},{"title":"How would habit look like if it was fun","target":"How would habit look like if it was fun","line":105},{"title":"Humans consistently overestimate the value or pleasure of what they don’t have and underestimate the pain or loss of losing something they do have.","target":"Humans consistently overestimate the value or pleasure of what they don’t have and underestimate the pain or loss of losing something they do have.","line":106},{"title":"I have never in my life learned anything from any man who agreed with me","target":"I have never in my life learned anything from any man who agreed with me","line":107},{"title":"I never doubted not only that I would get out, but also that I would prevail in the end and turn the experience into the defining event of my life, which, in retrospect, I would not trade.","target":"I never doubted not only that I would get out, but also that I would prevail in the end and turn the experience into the defining event of my life, which, in retrospect, I would not trade.","line":108},{"title":"I never doubted not only that I would get out, but also that I would prevail in the end and turn the experience into the defining event of my life, which, in retrospect, I would not trade.”","target":"I never doubted not only that I would get out, but also that I would prevail in the end and turn the experience into the defining event of my life, which, in retrospect, I would not trade.”","line":109},{"title":"I will have to remember I am here today to cross the swamp, not to fight all the alligators.","target":"I will have to remember I am here today to cross the swamp, not to fight all the alligators.","line":110},{"title":"If anyone can refute me—show me I'm making a mistake or looking at things from the wrong perspective—I'll gladly change. It's the truth I'm after. -Marcus Aurelius","target":"If anyone can refute me—show me I'm making a mistake or looking at things from the wrong perspective—I'll gladly change. It's the truth I'm after. -Marcus Aurelius","line":111},{"title":"If it's not Hell yes! it should be No.","target":"If it's not Hell yes! it should be No.","line":112},{"title":"If success is not making your life easier—or at least, providing you more autonomy—what good is it","target":"If success is not making your life easier—or at least, providing you more autonomy—what good is it","line":113},{"title":"If we take man as he is we make him worse. But if we take man as he should be we make him capable of becoming what he can be.","target":"If we take man as he is we make him worse. But if we take man as he should be we make him capable of becoming what he can be.","line":114},{"title":"If you ever find yourself in a hole, the first thing you do is stop digging.","target":"If you ever find yourself in a hole, the first thing you do is stop digging.","line":115},{"title":"If you focus on the obstacle all you'll see is obstacle","target":"If you focus on the obstacle all you'll see is obstacle","line":116},{"title":"If you have a friend whose friendship you wouldn't recommend to your sister, or your father, or your son, why would you have such a friend for yourself","target":"If you have a friend whose friendship you wouldn't recommend to your sister, or your father, or your son, why would you have such a friend for yourself","line":117},{"title":"if you want to reach a goal, you need to do two things- make the things that will help you reach the goal stronger, and reduce the things that will stop you from reaching the goal.","target":"if you want to reach a goal, you need to do two things- make the things that will help you reach the goal stronger, and reduce the things that will stop you from reaching the goal.","line":118},{"title":"If you wish to improve, be content to appear clueless or stupid in extraneous matters–don't wish to seem knowledgeable. –Epictetus","target":"If you wish to improve, be content to appear clueless or stupid in extraneous matters–don't wish to seem knowledgeable. –Epictetus","line":119},{"title":"If you're trying to hide your insecurities everybody will see it. When you open up and show your insecurities they dissappear.","target":"If you're trying to hide your insecurities everybody will see it. When you open up and show your insecurities they dissappear.","line":120},{"title":"Impact =- Productivity.  The Quest for Impact, Not Productivity","target":"Impact =- Productivity.  The Quest for Impact, Not Productivity","line":121},{"title":"In war, the victorious strategist only seeks battle after the victory has been won.” -Sun Tzu","target":"In war, the victorious strategist only seeks battle after the victory has been won.” -Sun Tzu","line":122},{"title":"Intentionally get it wrong. More mistakes you'll make inevitably get it right. Mistakes will show holes in understanding. Show which way to go next and help our creativity.","target":"Intentionally get it wrong. More mistakes you'll make inevitably get it right. Mistakes will show holes in understanding. Show which way to go next and help our creativity.","line":123},{"title":"Invert. Always Invert.” Oftentimes the best way to gain clarity about a problem is to address it backwards.","target":"Invert. Always Invert.” Oftentimes the best way to gain clarity about a problem is to address it backwards.","line":124},{"title":"Is easier to do something every day than a few times a week. Every day - default behavior","target":"Is easier to do something every day than a few times a week. Every day - default behavior","line":125},{"title":"It is not necessary to change a person in order to change their behavior. Just change their environment.","target":"It is not necessary to change a person in order to change their behavior. Just change their environment.","line":126},{"title":"It is not the strongest of the species that survives, nor the most intelligent. It is the one most adaptable to change.","target":"It is not the strongest of the species that survives, nor the most intelligent. It is the one most adaptable to change.","line":127},{"title":"It’s always better to start with a small local majority and, while we can’t control everything, we can control who we start with.","target":"It’s always better to start with a small local majority and, while we can’t control everything, we can control who we start with.","line":128},{"title":"It’s easier to practice self-restraint when you don’t have to use it.","target":"It’s easier to practice self-restraint when you don’t have to use it.","line":129},{"title":"It's important to sometimes slow down and ask Where am I going Isn't it just all speed without direction","target":"It's important to sometimes slow down and ask Where am I going Isn't it just all speed without direction","line":130},{"title":"It’s not the note you play that’s the wrong note—it’s the note you play afterwards that makes it right or wrong.","target":"It’s not the note you play that’s the wrong note—it’s the note you play afterwards that makes it right or wrong.","line":131},{"title":"It's not things themselves that disturb us but our interpretation of things.","target":"It's not things themselves that disturb us but our interpretation of things.","line":132},{"title":"It’s the strong swimmers who drown.","target":"It’s the strong swimmers who drown.","line":133},{"title":"JAK SE VYVAROVAT POHYBOVÝCH CHYB U MIMINEK DO 1 ROKU - BowenCentrum","target":"JAK SE VYVAROVAT POHYBOVÝCH CHYB U MIMINEK DO 1 ROKU - BowenCentrum","line":134},{"title":"Judge people by how well they treat those who can do nothing for them.","target":"Judge people by how well they treat those who can do nothing for them.","line":135},{"title":"Just because someone carries it well doesn't mean it isn't heavy. Everyone carries heavy load. Be kind to others.","target":"Just because someone carries it well doesn't mean it isn't heavy. Everyone carries heavy load. Be kind to others.","line":136},{"title":"Knowledge is subtractive, not additive—what we subtract (reduction by what does not work, what not to do), not what we add (what to do).","target":"Knowledge is subtractive, not additive—what we subtract (reduction by what does not work, what not to do), not what we add (what to do).","line":137},{"title":"Layer your skills -  If you can't win by being best, be different.","target":"Layer your skills -  If you can't win by being best, be different.","line":138},{"title":"Leader as counterweight for other people - bring people up when they are down and center them down when they are too distracted.","target":"Leader as counterweight for other people - bring people up when they are down and center them down when they are too distracted.","line":139},{"title":"Likelihood ratio - Any new information that challenges the idea we already hold lowers Likelihood of our believe being right.","target":"Likelihood ratio - Any new information that challenges the idea we already hold lowers Likelihood of our believe being right.","line":140},{"title":"Line up at least one task today with your mission, and things will happen.","target":"Line up at least one task today with your mission, and things will happen.","line":141},{"title":"Look for something that seems like work for others but not you.","target":"Look for something that seems like work for others but not you.","line":142},{"title":"Man feel love very differently from woman. Where woman crave love and affection as they're primary relationship needs, man desperately crave respect and admiration.","target":"Man feel love very differently from woman. Where woman crave love and affection as they're primary relationship needs, man desperately crave respect and admiration.","line":143},{"title":"Money plays an important role in life, but it can't be the only filter for how you decide to spend your time. Nobody will ever pay you to go on a date with your spouse or take your kids to the park or grab coffee with your parents.","target":"Money plays an important role in life, but it can't be the only filter for how you decide to spend your time. Nobody will ever pay you to go on a date with your spouse or take your kids to the park or grab coffee with your parents.","line":144},{"title":"Most of life is a search for who and what needs you the most.","target":"Most of life is a search for who and what needs you the most.","line":145},{"title":"Most of the embarrassing moments of my life happened when I wanted to say no, but ended up saying yes (or saying nothing at all).","target":"Most of the embarrassing moments of my life happened when I wanted to say no, but ended up saying yes (or saying nothing at all).","line":146},{"title":"Negative emotions are call to action","target":"Negative emotions are call to action","line":147},{"title":"Never be mean to person who could hurt you by doing nothing.","target":"Never be mean to person who could hurt you by doing nothing.","line":148},{"title":"New Research Reveals 9 Secrets That Will Make You An Expert Negotiator","target":"New Research Reveals 9 Secrets That Will Make You An Expert Negotiator","line":149},{"title":"Ninety percent of success can be boiled down to consistently doing the obvious thing for an uncommonly long period of time without convincing yourself that you're smarter than you are.","target":"Ninety percent of success can be boiled down to consistently doing the obvious thing for an uncommonly long period of time without convincing yourself that you're smarter than you are.","line":150},{"title":"No matter what they told me, I wouldn’t judge them. That I wouldn’t make them feel like lesser people for their mistakes. And because of that, they learned to trust me with their deepest thoughts.”","target":"No matter what they told me, I wouldn’t judge them. That I wouldn’t make them feel like lesser people for their mistakes. And because of that, they learned to trust me with their deepest thoughts.”","line":151},{"title":"No step is small, as long as it is headed in the direction of where we want to go.","target":"No step is small, as long as it is headed in the direction of where we want to go.","line":152},{"title":"On the way to a grand goal celebrate the smallest victories  as if each one were the final goal. That way, no matter where it ends  you are victorious.","target":"On the way to a grand goal celebrate the smallest victories  as if each one were the final goal. That way, no matter where it ends  you are victorious.","line":153},{"title":"People wont remember the words you say but how it made them feel.","target":"People wont remember the words you say but how it made them feel.","line":154},{"title":"Plans are worthless, but planning is essential.","target":"Plans are worthless, but planning is essential.","line":155},{"title":"Practice - get feedback on my progress; exercises with solution","target":"Practice - get feedback on my progress; exercises with solution","line":156},{"title":"Productivity is often a distraction. Don't aim for better ways to get through your tasks as quickly as possible, rather aim for better tasks that you never want to stop doing.","target":"Productivity is often a distraction. Don't aim for better ways to get through your tasks as quickly as possible, rather aim for better tasks that you never want to stop doing.","line":157},{"title":"puppy dog parenting","target":"puppy dog parenting","line":158},{"title":"Raise your ambitions. Lower your expectations. The higher your ambitions, the bolder your actions. The lower your expectations, the greater your satisfaction.","target":"Raise your ambitions. Lower your expectations. The higher your ambitions, the bolder your actions. The lower your expectations, the greater your satisfaction.","line":159},{"title":"Real world space repetition - telling your friend what you are learning about","target":"Real world space repetition - telling your friend what you are learning about","line":160},{"title":"Remove obstructions and make easier to do the right thing, habit.","target":"Remove obstructions and make easier to do the right thing, habit.","line":161},{"title":"Rephrase the notes you are taking","target":"Rephrase the notes you are taking","line":162},{"title":"Seek people whose lives are hard, and make it easier for them.","target":"Seek people whose lives are hard, and make it easier for them.","line":163},{"title":"Separating your decisions from your outcomes - What Can I Affect","target":"Separating your decisions from your outcomes - What Can I Affect","line":164},{"title":"So, attend carefully to your posture. Quit drooping and hunching around. Speak your mind. Put your desires forward, as if you had a right to them—at least the same right as others. Walk tall and gaze forthrightly ahead. Dare to be dangerous.","target":"So, attend carefully to your posture. Quit drooping and hunching around. Speak your mind. Put your desires forward, as if you had a right to them—at least the same right as others. Walk tall and gaze forthrightly ahead. Dare to be dangerous.","line":165},{"title":"Solve Problems Before They Happen by Developing an “Inner Sense of Captaincy”","target":"Solve Problems Before They Happen by Developing an “Inner Sense of Captaincy”","line":166},{"title":"Start with  ice-cream instead of the frog","target":"Start with  ice-cream instead of the frog","line":167},{"title":"Stress is good -or- bad for performance. Both is true based on what do you believe.","target":"Stress is good -or- bad for performance. Both is true based on what do you believe.","line":168},{"title":"Strong opinions held loosely","target":"Strong opinions held loosely","line":169},{"title":"The art of war teaches us to rely not on the likelihood of the enemy's not coming, but on our own readiness to receive him; not on the chance of his not attacking, but rather on the fact that we have made our position unassailable.” — Sun Tzu","target":"The art of war teaches us to rely not on the likelihood of the enemy's not coming, but on our own readiness to receive him; not on the chance of his not attacking, but rather on the fact that we have made our position unassailable.” — Sun Tzu","line":170},{"title":"The best argument against democracy is a five-minute conversation with the average voter.” -Winston Churchill","target":"The best argument against democracy is a five-minute conversation with the average voter.” -Winston Churchill","line":171},{"title":"The best generals are those who arrive at the results of planning without being tied to plans. - Winston Churchill","target":"The best generals are those who arrive at the results of planning without being tied to plans. - Winston Churchill","line":172},{"title":"The best way to cheer yourself up is to try to cheer somebody else up.","target":"The best way to cheer yourself up is to try to cheer somebody else up.","line":173},{"title":"The cold water doesn't get warmer if you jump late.","target":"The cold water doesn't get warmer if you jump late.","line":174},{"title":"The difference between good and great results is often found in consistently doing the boring things you know you should do exactly when you feel like doing them the least.","target":"The difference between good and great results is often found in consistently doing the boring things you know you should do exactly when you feel like doing them the least.","line":175},{"title":"The fact that you are fragile is actually a precondition to your heroism. If you weren't fragile there wouldn't be anything heroic about doing something difficult_","target":"The fact that you are fragile is actually a precondition to your heroism. If you weren't fragile there wouldn't be anything heroic about doing something difficult_","line":176},{"title":"The foundation of maturity - Just because it’s not your fault  doesn’t mean it’s not your responsibility.","target":"The foundation of maturity - Just because it’s not your fault  doesn’t mean it’s not your responsibility.","line":177},{"title":"The greatest victory is that which requires no battle.”  ― Sun Tzu, The Art of War","target":"The greatest victory is that which requires no battle.”  ― Sun Tzu, The Art of War","line":178},{"title":"The harder people have to work to understand you, the less they want your input.","target":"The harder people have to work to understand you, the less they want your input.","line":179},{"title":"the harder you work on offering other people what they need and want the more people will line up to play with you. -Jordan Peterson","target":"the harder you work on offering other people what they need and want the more people will line up to play with you. -Jordan Peterson","line":180},{"title":"The hardest thing in the world is to simplify your life because everything is pulling you to be more and more complex.” -Yvon Chouinard","target":"The hardest thing in the world is to simplify your life because everything is pulling you to be more and more complex.” -Yvon Chouinard","line":181},{"title":"The heaviest things in life are not iron or gold. It's unmade decisions. The reason you are stressed is you have decisions to make and you are not making them.","target":"The heaviest things in life are not iron or gold. It's unmade decisions. The reason you are stressed is you have decisions to make and you are not making them.","line":182},{"title":"The impulse to keep to yourself what you have learned is not only shameful, it's destructive. Anything you do not give freely and abundantly becomes lost to you, -Pulitzer Prize-winning author Annie Dillard.","target":"The impulse to keep to yourself what you have learned is not only shameful, it's destructive. Anything you do not give freely and abundantly becomes lost to you, -Pulitzer Prize-winning author Annie Dillard.","line":183},{"title":"the internet gave us access to everything but it also gave everything access to us –James Veitch","target":"the internet gave us access to everything but it also gave everything access to us –James Veitch","line":184},{"title":"The LORD will fight for you, and you only have to be silent.","target":"The LORD will fight for you, and you only have to be silent.","line":185},{"title":"The main thing is to keep the main thing the main thing_","target":"The main thing is to keep the main thing the main thing_","line":186},{"title":"The Myth of Self-Control","target":"The Myth of Self-Control","line":187},{"title":"The Paradox of Behavior Change","target":"The Paradox of Behavior Change","line":188},{"title":"The Price of Mistakes Varies in Time","target":"The Price of Mistakes Varies in Time","line":189},{"title":"The Stonecutter’s Credo","target":"The Stonecutter’s Credo","line":190},{"title":"The truly free individual is free only to the extent of his own self-mastery. While those who will not govern themselves are condemned to find masters to govern over them.  — Steven Pressfield, The War of Art","target":"The truly free individual is free only to the extent of his own self-mastery. While those who will not govern themselves are condemned to find masters to govern over them.  — Steven Pressfield, The War of Art","line":191},{"title":"the very strategies that parents use to try to keep their children safe – driving them around, maximizing supervision, and minimizing freedom – are unintentionally increasing the likelihood of injuries and even death.","target":"the very strategies that parents use to try to keep their children safe – driving them around, maximizing supervision, and minimizing freedom – are unintentionally increasing the likelihood of injuries and even death.","line":192},{"title":"The world will ask you who you are, and if you don't know, the world will tell you. - Carl Jung","target":"The world will ask you who you are, and if you don't know, the world will tell you. - Carl Jung","line":193},{"title":"Think about decisions like as bets","target":"Think about decisions like as bets","line":194},{"title":"Think of what is happening in your life.  You have power over it. Small but consistent changes in habits can have big impact on your average speed","target":"Think of what is happening in your life.  You have power over it. Small but consistent changes in habits can have big impact on your average speed","line":195},{"title":"This Unconventional Way of Consuming Books Will Transform How You Read","target":"This Unconventional Way of Consuming Books Will Transform How You Read","line":196},{"title":"This year, don’t ask yourself “What am I going to do to be a better man” or “What kind of man do I want to be” Invert those questions and ask “What am I NOT going to do to be a better man” and “What kind of man do I NOT want to be","target":"This year, don’t ask yourself “What am I going to do to be a better man” or “What kind of man do I want to be” Invert those questions and ask “What am I NOT going to do to be a better man” and “What kind of man do I NOT want to be","line":197},{"title":"Those who believe in free will are easiest to manipulate because they don't believe the can be manipulated","target":"Those who believe in free will are easiest to manipulate because they don't believe the can be manipulated","line":198},{"title":"Though not all stress can be reframed as a positive experience, you can proactively manage many external stressors, so they result in productive Eustress instead of paralysing distress.","target":"Though not all stress can be reframed as a positive experience, you can proactively manage many external stressors, so they result in productive Eustress instead of paralysing distress.","line":199},{"title":"To understand yourself reflect on everything you find irritating on others","target":"To understand yourself reflect on everything you find irritating on others","line":200},{"title":"Traffic test of relationship","target":"Traffic test of relationship","line":201},{"title":"Tři robotické zákony","target":"Tři robotické zákony","line":202},{"title":"Type 1 & Type 2 emotions","target":"Type 1 & Type 2 emotions","line":203},{"title":"U.S. Army’s Tactic to Fall Asleep in Two Minutes","target":"U.S. Army’s Tactic to Fall Asleep in Two Minutes","line":204},{"title":"Unspoken expectations are pre meditated resentments - Neil strauss","target":"Unspoken expectations are pre meditated resentments - Neil strauss","line":205},{"title":"We Make Everything Harder - zen habits zen habits","target":"We Make Everything Harder - zen habits zen habits","line":206},{"title":"What one takes most pain to do, should look as if it had been thrown off quickly, almost without effort.","target":"What one takes most pain to do, should look as if it had been thrown off quickly, almost without effort.","line":207},{"title":"What the wise man does in the beginning, the fool does in the end.","target":"What the wise man does in the beginning, the fool does in the end.","line":208},{"title":"When it comes to parenting, we need to ask ourselves not only what we could be doing more of, but also what we could be doing less of.","target":"When it comes to parenting, we need to ask ourselves not only what we could be doing more of, but also what we could be doing less of.","line":209},{"title":"When nothing is working, explore and make a lot of small bets.","target":"When nothing is working, explore and make a lot of small bets.","line":210},{"title":"When persuading - limit amount of selling points","target":"When persuading - limit amount of selling points","line":211},{"title":"When you buy something cheap and bad, the best youre going to feel about it is when you buy it. When you buy something expensive and good, the worst youre going to feel about it is when you buy it.","target":"When you buy something cheap and bad, the best youre going to feel about it is when you buy it. When you buy something expensive and good, the worst youre going to feel about it is when you buy it.","line":212},{"title":"When you fight something, youre tied to it forever. As long as youre fighting it, you are giving it power. You give it as much power as you are using to fight it.","target":"When you fight something, youre tied to it forever. As long as youre fighting it, you are giving it power. You give it as much power as you are using to fight it.","line":213},{"title":"When you write about things you read, it causes the value of your reading to increase exponentially. You don't just gain more knowledge, you're able to put into action.","target":"When you write about things you read, it causes the value of your reading to increase exponentially. You don't just gain more knowledge, you're able to put into action.","line":214},{"title":"Whenever you find yourself on the side of the majority, it is time to pause and reflect.”— Mark Twain","target":"Whenever you find yourself on the side of the majority, it is time to pause and reflect.”— Mark Twain","line":215},{"title":"Wishes for next generation","target":"Wishes for next generation","line":216},{"title":"Writing to be useful means writing what you would want to read. Simple, but not easy.","target":"Writing to be useful means writing what you would want to read. Simple, but not easy.","line":217},{"title":"You can be a victim or you can be a survivor.","target":"You can be a victim or you can be a survivor.","line":218},{"title":"You can be either angry or looking for solution. Not both at the same time.","target":"You can be either angry or looking for solution. Not both at the same time.","line":219},{"title":"You can be relaxed and dedicated. Just because you worry more, doesn't mean you care more.","target":"You can be relaxed and dedicated. Just because you worry more, doesn't mean you care more.","line":220},{"title":"You help people when they need help, not when you are ready to help them.","target":"You help people when they need help, not when you are ready to help them.","line":221},{"title":"You must never confuse faith that you will prevail in the end—which you can never afford to lose—with the discipline to confront the most brutal facts of your current reality, whatever they might be -Jim Stockdale","target":"You must never confuse faith that you will prevail in the end—which you can never afford to lose—with the discipline to confront the most brutal facts of your current reality, whatever they might be -Jim Stockdale","line":222},{"title":"#_000.General","target":"#_000.General","line":226}],"metadata":{"dg-publish":false,"date_saved":"2025-04-14","author":null,"linklist":null,"URL":null,"title":null},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},
